            <div class="modal__content type2">
                <header class="modal__header">
                    <h2 class="modal__title">메세지</h2>
                    <button class="modal__close">닫기</button>
                </header>
                <div class="modal__body">
                    <div class="subTit type2">
                        <h3>
                            한의사님의 기본 정보를 입력 하시면<br/>
                            입력 정보에 해당하는 한의사님을 찾아 드립니다.
                        </h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cont">
                        <div class="form" style="max-width:410px;margin:0 auto;">
                            <form action="">
                                <div class="row mb-4">
                                    <div class="col">
                                        <div class="input">
                                            <input type="text" placeholder="이름">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row mb-4">
                                    <div class="col">
                                        <div class="input">
                                            <input type="text" placeholder="이메일">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="row mb-4">
                                    <div class="col">
                                        <div class="input">
                                            <input type="text" placeholder="면허번호">
                                        </div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="action-box flex">
                                    <a href="" class="button small mint" style="width:100%;">등록</a>
                                </div>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                        <div class="result">
                            <div class="inner" style="max-width:410px;margin:0 auto;">
                                <div class="tit">결과</div>
                                <div class="txt">
                                    <div class="item">
                                        이름 : 홍길동<br/>
